This is a free set of slides for the text book "Modellierung and Optimierung with OPL"

The slides have been created with the LaTeX-Package beamer in pdflatex. They are divided into German and English versions, which are again devided by chapters. Each chapter can be compiled seperatly. 

Figures are made using LibreOffice draw and exported into pdfs. The pdfs contain the original odg file and can be easily modified.
